07:21.083 --> 07:26.804
Dear Sahajyogis

07:26.829 --> 07:37.235
and those who have curiosity to know about Sahajyoga

07:37.260 --> 07:43.794
Today

07:44.192 --> 07:51.754
it is a holy occassion.

07:51.779 --> 07:55.437
Shree Mataji Nirmala Deviji is with us

07:55.462 --> 08:09.732
and will tell us about Kundalini awakening

08:09.757 --> 08:13.810
I know that those gentlemen who have come here

08:13.835 --> 08:18.101
are having a great difficulty because of the lack of space

08:18.126 --> 08:21.682
i would like to be excused

08:21.707 --> 08:24.648
for the discomfort they will have on account of the shortage of space

08:24.714 --> 08:29.455
but what you will get

08:29.480 --> 08:32.373
in these sessions from Mataji

08:32.398 --> 08:35.223
that will overcome all that discomfort.

08:35.248 --> 08:37.773
This is what i assure you

08:37.798 --> 08:39.434
but along with that

08:39.460 --> 08:45.455
What shall i say

08:45.480 --> 08:51.130
in appreciation of this compassionate and loving Mother

08:51.155 --> 08:53.365
can't say anything, can't understand anything,

08:53.390 --> 08:57.960
from where shall i start and how shall i start

08:59.500 --> 09:05.915
Mother, who is the source and ocean of compassion and  love

09:05.939 --> 09:09.233
who is sitting here among us

09:10.205 --> 09:19.181
To that thing for which our saints had said

09:19.208 --> 09:24.256
that Kundalini awakening is very tough

09:24.281 --> 09:28.599
and takes place only after a great effort.

09:28.624 --> 09:34.336
But Mother has made it so easy.

09:34.361 --> 09:41.352
If you are really eager to know or are seekers

09:41.377 --> 09:48.119
i assure you that today, before leaving this place

09:48.143 --> 09:50.652
you will get your realization. Thank you.

09:50.677 --> 09:53.899
without coming too much in between you and Mataji

09:53.924 --> 09:55.357
i shall request Mataji

09:55.382 --> 10:02.336
that She with Her compassionate and loving voice

10:02.361 --> 10:08.482
shall satisfy your inner desire.

10:08.507 --> 10:13.341
CLAPPING

10:13.366 --> 10:37.898
Shree Mataji, stands up to talk to seekers.

10:37.923 --> 10:40.346
The seekers of truth

10:46.719 --> 10:53.782
I bow respectfully to all the souls.

10:53.808 --> 10:59.952
Today I was thinking, in which language I should converse with you

10:59.977 --> 11:01.281
So, I thought that

11:01.306 --> 11:05.889
I have given speeches many times in Marathi in Poona

11:05.914 --> 11:08.898
and today let Me speak in Hindi

11:08.923 --> 11:14.080
as Hindi is our national Language.

11:14.105 --> 11:16.604
And My mother tongue is Marathi

11:16.629 --> 11:20.941
but I think that, learning Hindi language is most important.

11:20.966 --> 11:28.984
So you, lovers of Marathi Language, plz forgive Me liberally.

11:29.009 --> 11:33.539
and Hindi speaking people, who are literary

11:33.564 --> 11:37.854
also please forgive Me for My mistakes, if there are any.

11:37.879 --> 11:42.945
But first of all, you must understand that language should be of heart

11:42.970 --> 11:47.888
where language instead of being of heart, is only unintelligible

11:47.913 --> 11:52.272
then all types of troubles crop up.

11:52.297 --> 11:55.519
That is why any language which comes out of heart

11:55.544 --> 11:58.883
is touching and is effective.

11:58.908 --> 12:04.519
We have been in search of truth for the past so many years.

12:04.547 --> 12:06.342
It is not just today only.

12:06.367 --> 12:09.712
We have been in search of truth for the past so many years

12:09.737 --> 12:17.559
and in this process of search, many people have gone astray.

12:17.584 --> 12:20.254
We should understand its reason

12:20.279 --> 12:25.304
because today's situation, today's environment and today's atmosphere

12:25.329 --> 12:28.403
in that atmosphere one cannot understand that

12:28.428 --> 12:32.775
everybody talks about God, talk about dharma.

12:32.800 --> 12:34.013
Why do they create, so much dispute

12:34.038 --> 12:37.908
so much disaster and such a scene?

12:37.933 --> 12:43.632
This question arises in front of younger generation

12:43.657 --> 12:47.602
and they ask repeatedly, "Mother what does it mean?"

12:47.627 --> 12:55.914
If God is truth, if God is love, if God is kindness

12:55.939 --> 12:59.672
it doesn't seem, that there is any such blessing of God

12:59.697 --> 13:02.419
or there is any effect of God.

13:02.444 --> 13:08.495
So it is better to forget such God, who has created so much fuss.

13:08.520 --> 13:11.856
In this way, you can see that a big tussle is going on

13:11.881 --> 13:16.457
among our younger generation.

13:16.482 --> 13:19.162
The discussion is on, about God's existence.

13:19.187 --> 13:22.373
How to come to an agreement?

13:22.398 --> 13:26.814
You may agree or not, but there is God.

13:26.839 --> 13:29.363
It is not a question of agreement or disagreement.

13:29.388 --> 13:34.021
The truth will be, whether you accept it or not.

13:34.046 --> 13:38.580
But what is it that happened, because of which

13:38.605 --> 13:41.392
man follows wrong  paths

13:41.417 --> 13:45.209
where you do not find God even by searching.

13:45.657 --> 13:48.862
If we try to understand this

13:48.887 --> 13:52.314
Where did we make the mistake should be visible to us.

13:52.339 --> 13:58.507
Now  Sahajyoga is: Sahaja: Saha means 'with you', 'ja', means 'born'.

13:58.532 --> 14:03.975
Now the programme of Divine connection born with you

14:04.000 --> 14:07.755
which for you is the strategy of Divine connection

14:07.780 --> 14:11.128
not only this, it is an assurance for you.

14:11.153 --> 14:14.132
The time has come to prove that .

14:14.157 --> 14:16.817
Sahajyoga is not today's discovery.

14:16.842 --> 14:18.517
Thousand years back also

14:18.542 --> 14:23.682
Indra was given self realization and self knowledge.

14:23.707 --> 14:25.648
Even then there was Sahajyoga

14:25.673 --> 14:28.676
and after that you have seen that Markandey Swami

14:28.701 --> 14:31.489
who had come in this world 14000 years before

14:31.514 --> 14:34.349
also has said about the importance of Sahaj.

14:34.374 --> 14:37.446
But did not say it openly.

14:37.471 --> 14:42.129
After that, we can say that after many years

14:42.154 --> 14:47.737
Adi Shankaracharya openly talked about it to all the societies.

14:47.762 --> 14:49.564
Even then it was not said

14:49.589 --> 14:51.216
that how it happens.

14:51.241 --> 14:52.761
It was not fully explained

14:52.786 --> 14:54.256
because that was not the time.

14:54.281 --> 14:58.138
Krishna also said, that you should know Atma

14:58.163 --> 15:01.006
the one who has known his self, only can understand

15:01.031 --> 15:04.316
Christ also said, that there should be your second birth.

15:04.341 --> 15:07.571
Buddha, Mahavira, everybody said that

15:07.596 --> 15:09.713
there should be your second birth.

15:09.738 --> 15:13.557
But Adi Shankaracharya told it very openly

15:13.582 --> 15:16.217
that apart from this there is no other way.

15:16.242 --> 15:20.040
Unless cool vibrations will flow from within you

15:20.065 --> 15:23.138
till then he said, "SALEELAM, SALEELAM"

15:23.163 --> 15:26.134
we cannot get rid of this web of words.

15:26.159 --> 15:30.725
But I will say that Nanak Sahab and Kabirdas ji

15:30.750 --> 15:36.483
tried their best and presented the truth that

15:36.508 --> 15:40.204
without the awakening of Kundalini, nothing can be proved.

15:40.229 --> 15:45.501
But their way of talking was so emphatic and so strong

15:45.526 --> 15:47.815
that people could not understand them.

15:47.960 --> 15:50.648
This is what I felt that

15:50.673 --> 15:54.127
in this world, unless you give them knowledge of the self

15:54.152 --> 15:58.382
it will be almost useless to talk about it.

15:58.406 --> 16:02.616
For example, Gita was written. But the readers were mislead.

16:02.641 --> 16:04.999
After that, some thing more about knowledge was written.

16:05.024 --> 16:07.246
That too mislead the readers.

16:07.271 --> 16:10.534
But now it is, not to do anything

16:10.559 --> 16:12.583
to show anything or to say anything

16:12.608 --> 16:14.446
and keeping that in mind

16:14.471 --> 16:21.211
I have tried to find out, what are the problems of mankind?

16:21.236 --> 16:23.381
What are the obstacles?

16:23.406 --> 16:26.509
Because of which, he cannot recognize God

16:26.534 --> 16:30.223
and after working hard for a long period of My life

16:30.248 --> 16:32.737
one day, spontaneously I thought that

16:32.762 --> 16:35.228
by opening Sahastrara, everything will be alright

16:35.253 --> 16:39.034
and that is how our Sahajyoga was established.

16:39.059 --> 16:43.309
Now in nutshell, you must understand

16:43.334 --> 16:46.165
that this is a living process within us, a living process.

16:46.190 --> 16:50.213
As we have become human beings from an amoeba

16:50.238 --> 16:51.398
in the same way

16:51.423 --> 16:54.940
we have to become from a human being to a realized person

16:54.965 --> 16:57.456
and that too by a living process.

16:57.482 --> 17:00.288
There is no artificiality in it

17:00.313 --> 17:07.623
that it will happen by a bundle of words.

17:07.648 --> 17:09.777
it is an activity within the being.

17:09.802 --> 17:15.570
For example, if you want to grow a seed

17:15.595 --> 17:18.381
if sprout, has to come out

17:18.406 --> 17:21.245
you will have to put it in the heart of the mother

17:21.270 --> 17:26.910
you will have to put it into the womb of a mother earth.

17:26.935 --> 17:30.688
It gets sprouted, can you say how?

17:30.713 --> 17:34.026
You cannot say ,how a flower turns into a fruit.

17:34.051 --> 17:38.379
In this way, Sahajyoga

17:38.404 --> 17:40.504
is a strange happening

17:40.529 --> 17:44.323
but I can tell you, how it takes place.

17:44.348 --> 17:48.426
Because man's all workings must be known.

17:48.451 --> 17:52.890
So, you can know that within us the power of Kundalini

17:52.915 --> 17:56.997
which is settled in triangular bone

17:57.022 --> 18:00.977
when awakened, gives self realization.

18:01.002 --> 18:05.076
It is so surprising that while writing Geeta

18:05.101 --> 18:08.105
Gneshwari has been written, completely based on Geeta only

18:08.130 --> 18:15.917
Gyaneshwar ji in sixth chapter emphatically explained Kundalini.

18:15.942 --> 18:19.181
He has talked about it, discussed it and explained it beautifully

18:19.206 --> 18:21.003
Very beautifully explained

18:21.028 --> 18:25.719
and he has also said that when Kundalini will be awakened

18:25.744 --> 18:27.924
then people will be benifitted in such ways

18:27.949 --> 18:30.281
In that a very beautiful thing is

18:30.306 --> 18:33.187
Zo Jey Wanchele Te To laho

18:33.212 --> 18:34.907
you will get whatever you desire

18:34.932 --> 18:37.160
But a man's desire itself changes.

18:37.185 --> 18:40.299
His behaviour of desiring itself changes.

18:40.324 --> 18:43.410
Now, this Kundalini is situated within us.

18:43.435 --> 18:45.949
Now, if there are scientific people

18:45.974 --> 18:48.893
they will say, " How did you know this?"

18:48.918 --> 18:53.541
I know it, whether you agree or disagree

18:53.566 --> 18:57.703
but even if you are a scientist, you should keep your brain open.

18:57.728 --> 18:59.418
You should have open mindedness.

18:59.443 --> 19:02.744
If you are not open minded, you can never be a scientist.

19:02.769 --> 19:08.890
I am presenting a hypothesis before you

19:08.915 --> 19:12.770
if I prove that, then it becomes a rule.

19:12.795 --> 19:17.856
In the same way, Kundalini is a deep subject.

19:17.881 --> 19:22.030
and to acquire that deep subject, we must keep our mind open.

19:22.055 --> 19:24.465
If beforehand only, you stand with rods in your hands

19:24.490 --> 19:26.180
what shall I say?

19:26.205 --> 19:30.407
I have seen that such things happen only in the kingdom of God.

19:30.432 --> 19:33.518
You see, if you are going to join a college or a university

19:33.543 --> 19:35.795
how much do you struggle for admission?

19:35.820 --> 19:38.956
How many hurdles we overcome, to take admission

19:38.981 --> 19:42.406
we take admission and sit in front of our teachers

19:42.431 --> 19:43.353
with our necks bend down

19:43.378 --> 19:45.619
taking it for granted that whatever they will say, will be valid.

19:45.644 --> 19:50.251
But I have seen that all the saints who came into this world

19:50.276 --> 19:52.914
were tortured by us

19:52.939 --> 19:55.756
troubled them, did not listen to them

19:55.780 --> 20:02.707
bothered them and every time argumented with them.

20:02.732 --> 20:07.381
In this way, you cannot get knowledge.

20:07.406 --> 20:09.519
For getting knowledge, the first thing is that

20:09.544 --> 20:13.627
i have no knowledge and i have to know now.

20:13.652 --> 20:19.411
In all the Shastras, all the great saints have written about that.

20:19.436 --> 20:22.310
Ramdas Swami has clearly written that

20:22.335 --> 20:24.676
by reading, nothing is going to be achieved.

20:25.252 --> 20:28.458
Our Kabirdas ji has clearly written

20:28.483 --> 20:33.357
Padi Padi Pandit Moorakh Bhai.

20:33.382 --> 20:34.744
He has written clearly

20:34.769 --> 20:38.659
and lot of things these saints have written very clearly

20:38.684 --> 20:41.816
it is so surprising that we read their books

20:41.841 --> 20:44.911
how do we do only, what they have forbidden.

20:44.936 --> 20:49.623
Now, I will tell you the reason as to why that happens

20:49.648 --> 20:56.904
and because of this how our dharma somehow changes into adharma.

20:56.929 --> 21:00.060
Kundalini Shakti is pure desire.

21:00.125 --> 21:05.481
This is pure desire means all other desires are impure desires.

21:05.506 --> 21:07.206
Because had it not been impure

21:07.231 --> 21:08.645
on getting one

21:08.670 --> 21:10.578
there would not have been the desire for getting other things.

21:10.603 --> 21:16.722
According to the laws of our Economics, laws of Artha Shastra

21:16.747 --> 21:20.501
any type of necessity is not fullfilled normally.

21:20.526 --> 21:25.095
Means in general these cannot be satisfied.

21:25.120 --> 21:29.896
In general, means that if you get one thing in particular

21:29.921 --> 21:31.388
but after getting that

21:31.427 --> 21:34.167
if you want to get second thing and then third thing

21:34.192 --> 21:37.953
its reason is that you don't have pure desire.

21:38.059 --> 21:42.629
The desire for which you strive hard to be fullfilled

21:42.654 --> 21:45.049
that desire is not pure desire, it is impure desire.

21:45.073 --> 21:50.640
The power of pure desire is this Kundalini, which has made this PINDA

21:50.665 --> 21:52.827
and after that is sitting just like that

21:52.852 --> 21:55.008
because it has not been awakened as yet

21:55.033 --> 22:00.889
it has not been manifested perfectly within us, as yet

22:00.914 --> 22:02.474
so that it shows its effect.

22:02.499 --> 22:06.307
This pure desire is settled in our triangular bone

22:06.332 --> 22:10.786
which we call  kundalini because it has three and a half circles.

22:10.811 --> 22:12.268
Why is she sitting in three and a half circle

22:12.293 --> 22:13.629
what is the mathematical explanation of it, etc.

22:13.654 --> 22:16.889
I don't have that much time today, to explain it

22:16.914 --> 22:18.833
If you listen to My lectures

22:18.858 --> 22:22.076
you will find that, I have explained everything very clearly.

22:22.101 --> 22:25.640
Now, this power of Kundalini is Pure Desire.

22:25.665 --> 22:31.610
So the pure desire when awakened within us, what do we see

22:31.635 --> 22:34.532
that while passing through our chakras inside our being

22:34.557 --> 22:41.950
it remains unattatched and nourishes nicely to our chakras

22:41.975 --> 22:46.121
and if we look at it logically, it is right

22:46.146 --> 22:48.023
that inside a tree

22:48.048 --> 22:53.552
when its inner fluid (sap) grows and clings to any spot

22:53.577 --> 22:55.723
and if it dies, even in any one thing

22:55.748 --> 22:59.231
the tree as well as that thing will be dead.

22:59.256 --> 23:03.669
In the same way, when this Kundalini awakens within us

23:03.694 --> 23:05.570
and starts moving ahead

23:05.595 --> 23:09.999
this pure desire, keeps away other impure desires.

23:10.024 --> 23:14.079
But our routine remined just the opposite of it

23:14.104 --> 23:16.542
when we took a turn towards dharma.

23:16.567 --> 23:19.093
First of all, when we take a turn towards dharma

23:19.118 --> 23:21.372
or towards anything

23:21.397 --> 23:25.941
first, our physical relation comes in contact with them.

23:25.966 --> 23:30.785
We analyse what physical or material benifits we can get out of it.

23:30.809 --> 23:33.773
We see, as soon as people come to our house

23:33.798 --> 23:36.947
first of all we observe, what beniffits we can have out of it.

23:36.971 --> 23:38.333
What can we do with it?

23:38.358 --> 23:39.840
Even people think that

23:39.865 --> 23:45.792
it is better that we grab somebody's money, do this, do that

23:45.817 --> 23:47.711
and then by and by

23:47.736 --> 23:49.817
such things start taking shape

23:49.842 --> 23:52.699
which are virtually rubbish and hellish.

23:52.724 --> 23:54.558
The attention goes towards body.

23:54.583 --> 23:57.027
When a man's attention goes towards his body

23:57.052 --> 23:58.605
then it is not in his pure desire.

23:58.630 --> 24:00.041
It is so simple.

24:00.065 --> 24:03.830
then in the body, then change the dresses, change the name

24:03.855 --> 24:05.366
and do all types of worldly things

24:05.391 --> 24:07.675
can not establish dharma.

24:07.700 --> 24:10.792
So, man went on going astray

24:10.817 --> 24:14.456
so, the second catch that a man gets and is a very strong catch

24:14.481 --> 24:17.310
that is mental, means on wisdom.

24:17.334 --> 24:20.208
(NOT CLEAR) you know that

24:20.233 --> 24:26.706
how much, one very great intellectualist, tortured Adi Shankaracharya

24:26.731 --> 24:28.704
Always such intellectualists

24:28.729 --> 24:30.425
never understand how much they adhere to their intellect.

24:30.450 --> 24:33.261
They adhere to what they read

24:33.286 --> 24:35.674
If any one has read Gita

24:35.699 --> 24:38.730
he thinks, that he has become Vyas Munni atleast.

24:38.755 --> 24:41.792
if not greater than him but atleast i have become Vyas Munni.

24:41.817 --> 24:44.133
If somebody reads Bible, he feels that

24:44.158 --> 24:46.749
he thinks that Christ knows better than him

24:46.774 --> 24:50.062
This intellectual catch when it comes within us

24:50.087 --> 24:51.890
that gives rise to all the more questions.

24:51.915 --> 24:53.670
This whole Christian religion

24:53.695 --> 24:57.609
has come to an end because of this intellectual catch.

24:57.634 --> 25:01.499
You visualise how this intellectual catch came into it.

25:01.524 --> 25:04.223
When Christ came into this world

25:04.248 --> 25:06.655
He said ,"Take your rebirth."

25:06.680 --> 25:07.961
At that time Nicodemus said

25:07.986 --> 25:10.882
"Shall i enter again into my mother's womb?"

25:10.907 --> 25:14.593
He (Christ) said, "No,he who takes birth from womb, he is still JADDA."

25:14.618 --> 25:19.308
"But one takes birth from ATMA, from ADISHAKTI only is atma."

25:19.333 --> 25:23.370
unless you know atma, you cannot know God.

25:23.395 --> 25:26.293
But they thought that it was not clear

25:26.318 --> 25:31.324
because none of them knew to give realization

25:31.349 --> 25:32.911
Anyway, even if they didn't know

25:32.936 --> 25:36.779
there was no need of making a mess of intellectuality.

25:37.020 --> 25:38.753
He made such a mess of intellectualism

25:38.778 --> 25:41.112
there was a person named St. Paul

25:41.137 --> 25:43.560
who had no link with Christian Religion

25:43.585 --> 25:45.045
He had not seen Christ

25:45.070 --> 25:47.838
He himself was epileptic and used to be sick

25:47.863 --> 25:51.141
and in My view he had some Supraconscious problems

25:51.166 --> 25:53.048
he took his entry in Bible.

25:53.073 --> 25:54.954
When I first read Bible

25:54.979 --> 25:56.501
I asked ,"who is this gentleman?"

25:56.526 --> 25:59.775
Not only I, Khalil Jibran, and so many people

25:59.800 --> 26:04.360
You must be knowing that William Blake was a great seer.

26:04.385 --> 26:07.881
At that time, he said why is this (Mr. Paul) in Bible?

26:07.906 --> 26:10.159
And after they settled him in Bible

26:10.184 --> 26:13.846
whatever he wrote about Bible, they validated.

26:13.871 --> 26:16.320
Now he is in such a condition

26:16.345 --> 26:22.738
that, when an intellectual came across Bible and came to know that

26:22.763 --> 26:25.773
Paul, has not written anything about the birth of Jesus

26:25.798 --> 26:27.774
had not written anything about his mother.

26:27.799 --> 26:31.234
He didn't write anything about his miracles.

26:31.259 --> 26:36.905
He said that his disciples were fishermen

26:36.930 --> 26:39.788
would catch fishes and were fish killers.

26:39.812 --> 26:40.883
He didn't have any wisdom.

26:40.908 --> 26:43.409
He said so, just from from his own mind

26:43.434 --> 26:48.617
and to support this, Bishop of Cantebury

26:48.642 --> 26:52.058
too had to help him and say that it is okay.

26:52.083 --> 26:55.538
So, now you either follow Paul or Jesus.

26:55.563 --> 26:58.061
He (Bishop of Cantebury) said that he (Paul) is right.

26:58.086 --> 27:00.284
'Jesus was born', was wrong

