and he made an intellectual and argumentative Christian Religion

27:13.030 --> 27:14.170
that whatever may happen

27:14.195 --> 27:15.344
even at the cost of holding guns in hands

27:15.369 --> 27:16.610
would convert everyone to a Christian.

27:16.635 --> 27:19.895
To become a Christian means to become a Sahajyogi.

27:19.920 --> 27:22.130
To become a Yogi.

27:22.155 --> 27:24.116
Same is the case with Muslims.

27:24.141 --> 27:26.281
What Mohammad Sahab had written

27:26.306 --> 27:29.565
was turned so much upside down and made Muslim religion.

27:29.590 --> 27:31.296
The same is the case with Hindus.

27:31.321 --> 27:33.296
The situation of Hindus is the very bad.

27:33.321 --> 27:34.843
Because they didn't create one dharma

27:34.868 --> 27:35.786
they created fifty dharmas.

27:35.810 --> 27:39.488
I can't understand when shall we learn a lesson.

27:39.513 --> 27:43.789
First of all, it has been said that Atma lies in everyone.

27:43.814 --> 27:45.875
Then how was caste system evolved?

27:45.900 --> 27:48.117
Caste system has no meaning

27:48.142 --> 27:52.187
because caste system was created on the basis of profession.

27:52.212 --> 27:54.539
and since this caste system was made on the basis of birth

27:54.564 --> 27:56.074
this mess started.

27:56.099 --> 28:00.182
It is not possible at all that it will be according to birth

28:00.207 --> 28:03.645
Vyas wrote Geeta. who was Vyas?

28:03.670 --> 28:08.250
Everybody knows that he was the son of a  DIMARNI, who was not married.

28:08.275 --> 28:09.908
Can he be a Brahmin?

28:09.933 --> 28:13.559
Valmiki, who wrote Valmiki Ramayana, who was he?

28:13.584 --> 28:17.179
The great people who wrote Shastras, who were they?

28:17.204 --> 28:20.758
Brahmin is he who knows Bramha.

28:20.783 --> 28:23.608
Those who don't know Bramha, cannot be called Bramha.

28:23.633 --> 28:26.883
But we are Brahmins by birth, even though we may do any work

28:26.908 --> 28:28.823
We have become (Brahmins) by birth, okay.

28:28.848 --> 28:32.117
Now even our elections are also held on the basis of Caste system

28:32.142 --> 28:34.074
So, may God protect this country.

28:34.099 --> 28:35.403
What shall be its result?

28:35.428 --> 28:37.656
Because the caste in which you are born

28:37.681 --> 28:39.890
JAA-TI, Jati means Sahaj.

28:39.915 --> 28:43.368
Sahaj, that which is Sahaj (spontaneous) in you

28:43.392 --> 28:46.844
One who is in search of God is Brahmin

28:46.869 --> 28:52.016
and the person who seeks joy in bussiness is Vaishya.

28:52.041 --> 28:53.969
In this way, all the castes were classified

28:53.994 --> 28:56.867
and so much importance was given to those castes

28:56.892 --> 28:59.399
that we had Gora Kumbhar.

28:59.424 --> 29:02.820
In this Maharashtra, there is so much alertness

29:02.845 --> 29:05.704
they have made his full statue, Gora became Kumbhar.

29:05.729 --> 29:06.893
Tukaram said

29:06.918 --> 29:07.821
"It would have been better

29:07.846 --> 29:08.916
had i become MAHAAR(untouchable)."

29:08.941 --> 29:13.338
All the saints repeatedly spoke against caste system

29:13.363 --> 29:16.097
Not only this, Gyaneshwar Ji was tortured.

29:16.122 --> 29:19.473
All these intellectuals who considered themselves as

29:19.498 --> 29:23.709
entrepreneurs of God, everything and that of religion

29:23.734 --> 29:25.257
tortured them ( Saints) badly.

29:25.282 --> 29:27.099
And now they are writing his Gyaneshwari.

29:27.124 --> 29:28.180
He is being worshipped.

29:28.205 --> 29:29.645
They are making a temple of Gyaneshwar Ji.

29:31.666 --> 29:32.740
Its reason is that

29:32.765 --> 29:38.046
there was a great need of intellectual intelligence and not of Spirit

29:38.071 --> 29:39.627
There should be knowledge of spirit.

29:39.652 --> 29:43.154
All the saints have said, "Recognize your spirit."

29:43.224 --> 29:50.014
Namdev Sahab who was a great poet and had limitless knowledge.

29:50.039 --> 29:54.017
He has written a beautiful poetry

29:54.042 --> 29:56.703
Which was recognized by Nanak Sahab

29:56.728 --> 29:59.217
and included in Guru Granth Sahab

29:59.242 --> 30:01.168
which I will explain you in Hindi.

30:01.193 --> 30:06.672
He says that when a person gets one with God

30:06.697 --> 30:11.658
his condition is like a child whose attention is on a kite

30:11.683 --> 30:13.312
he is flying.

30:13.337 --> 30:15.469
the kite is fluttering in the sky

30:15.494 --> 30:17.340
He used Marathi word 'FARARI' (flutter)

30:17.365 --> 30:19.577
the kite is spinning after fluttering

30:19.757 --> 30:22.761
and this child is talking to others

30:22.786 --> 30:24.608
playing and running forward and backward

30:24.633 --> 30:29.987
but at that time, his attention is on that kite.

30:30.012 --> 30:31.927
Second thing, he said that

30:31.952 --> 30:35.776
when the ladies return back after filling their pitches (with water)

30:35.801 --> 30:39.208
are walking faster and talking among themselves

30:39.233 --> 30:41.352
and their pots are on their heads

30:41.377 --> 30:44.366
laughing and joking is going on, among themselves

30:44.391 --> 30:47.169
but, their attention is on the pot on their heads.

30:47.194 --> 30:49.409
So, it is worth understanding

30:49.434 --> 30:51.239
that those who are talking about dharma

30:51.264 --> 30:54.460
should get their self realization first.

30:54.485 --> 30:57.683
Otherwise, they don't have any right to get their self realization.

30:57.708 --> 31:04.151
And have no right to say that they are self realized.

31:04.176 --> 31:06.979
They may say to themselves that they are very great

31:07.004 --> 31:08.618
and give self certificate to themselves

31:08.643 --> 31:10.990
but its recognition is that

31:11.015 --> 31:14.535
a realized person must have

31:14.560 --> 31:17.045
collective consciousness inside his being.

31:17.070 --> 31:18.819
He should have collective consciousness inside his being.

31:18.844 --> 31:21.561
If he doesn't have that collective consciousness inside his being

31:21.586 --> 31:24.018
how much self certifition he may give himself

31:24.043 --> 31:26.826
even then he is not a self realized soul.

31:26.851 --> 31:29.067
And it is important that

31:29.092 --> 31:30.751
the nurturers of dharma

31:30.776 --> 31:34.866
those who can maintain dharma, should be self realized.

31:34.891 --> 31:37.485
It is only their right to discuss about dharma.

31:37.510 --> 31:40.982
Those who have not received that light till now

31:41.007 --> 31:43.310
have not received the light of the spirit

31:43.335 --> 31:46.583
those who are standing in the dark, what shall they talk about

31:46.608 --> 31:48.164
there will be discussion only about darkness

31:48.189 --> 31:50.695
or what shall a blind man say

31:50.720 --> 31:53.410
which colours or which art is lying here?

31:53.435 --> 31:57.194
So first, one's own eyes should get opened

31:57.219 --> 32:01.320
and that eye can be known only through the vision of the spirit.

32:01.345 --> 32:03.907
Even in Gita it is written, ATMANE  ATMANE TUSHTAHA

32:03.932 --> 32:05.931
Atma gets satisfied only by atma.

32:09.339 --> 32:13.323
Third catch is the worst, useless!

32:13.348 --> 32:17.315
in which, a person gets attatched to someone by his emotions

32:17.340 --> 32:20.948
emotions which we sometimes take for SHRADHA.

32:20.973 --> 32:22.846
But this is not SHRADHA, this is blind devotion.

32:22.871 --> 32:25.049
People move with blind devotion.

32:25.074 --> 32:26.709
Blind devotion means such

32:26.734 --> 32:28.795
When Jesus came

32:28.820 --> 32:32.370
people said that, we follow Moses because Moses had died.

32:32.395 --> 32:35.543
Now we follow Moses, we don't believe in Jesus.

32:35.568 --> 32:39.240
For example, Jews said we don't believe in Jesus

32:39.265 --> 32:41.053
We believe only in Moses.

32:41.078 --> 32:42.927
At that time Moses was not there.

32:42.952 --> 32:46.438
And that is why, Moses had said that we should suffer

32:46.463 --> 32:48.766
So, we will suffer

32:48.791 --> 32:51.811
although our whole suffering was about to come to an end.

32:51.836 --> 32:53.667
But they said," No, we will suffer".

32:53.692 --> 32:56.687
So, it is okay! Hitler came for you, and you better suffer.

32:56.712 --> 33:01.261
This was their basic difference, that we must suffer.

