Now what you have to suffer?

33:03.177 --> 33:06.515
What wrong things you have been taught?

33:06.540 --> 33:10.575
That you have to suffer always.

33:10.600 --> 33:13.844
God, who has given you this man's body

33:13.869 --> 33:17.315
why should He give you trouble and worries?

33:17.340 --> 33:21.829
When your mother gave you birth, she took all the trouble

33:21.854 --> 33:23.722
she didn't give you any trouble.

33:23.747 --> 33:26.030
Then to raise such issues

33:26.055 --> 33:27.978
in our Maharashtra, this is very special

33:28.003 --> 33:29.804
today is Monday and so it is fast day

