tomorrow is tuesday, and so fast day

33:31.471 --> 33:33.267
next day is wednesday and so fast day

33:33.292 --> 33:34.937
and something other, so fasting day.

33:34.962 --> 33:36.870
That means in our country, there are so many people fasting

33:36.895 --> 33:38.189
so why do you fast?

33:38.214 --> 33:41.303
But in our country, there is a disease of keeping fasts

33:41.328 --> 33:42.809
that too they will do in those days

33:42.834 --> 33:48.921
the day our some great incarnations took birth.

33:48.946 --> 33:52.255
For example, in our country, we observe SANKASHTI

33:52.280 --> 33:53.501
the day when Ganeshji was born.

33:53.526 --> 33:54.527
That day they will keep fast.

33:54.552 --> 33:57.991
If a child is born in your house, will you keep fast

33:58.016 --> 33:58.767
or observe SUTAK ( Impurity arising to the members of a family on account of that birth )

33:58.792 --> 34:01.955
or distribute sweets.

34:01.980 --> 34:04.647
Everything upside down they would talk

34:04.672 --> 34:09.497
that by being emotional, by torturing ourselves, we can know God.

34:09.522 --> 34:12.812
We know God by torturing ourselves

34:12.837 --> 34:13.805
as Shiyas do.

34:13.830 --> 34:15.982
People are absolutely mistaken.

34:16.007 --> 34:19.271
On the contrary, those who are joyful, they only can know God.

34:19.296 --> 34:20.617
For example, in English it is said

34:20.642 --> 34:22.393
"Count your blessings one by one ".

34:22.418 --> 34:24.164
Those who think of the blessings

34:24.189 --> 34:25.583
"How much God has given me".

34:25.608 --> 34:27.013
He gets connected to God.

34:27.038 --> 34:29.818
One who sees oneself in  distress

34:29.843 --> 34:32.759
you only say, if any mother sees her child

34:32.784 --> 34:34.536
that he is dying of hunger

34:34.561 --> 34:36.794
what can be more distressing than this, for a mother.

34:36.819 --> 34:38.589
She will say that my birth has been useless

34:38.614 --> 34:40.310
if my child remains hungry.

34:40.335 --> 34:42.560
There can be nothing more painful that this.

34:42.585 --> 34:45.466
Okay, if you want to fast, do so there is no harm

34:45.491 --> 34:47.396
you do it for your good health

34:47.421 --> 34:50.234
but there is no need to fast, in the name of God.

34:50.259 --> 34:53.521
This emotional feeling, that we are very sad.

34:53.546 --> 34:57.453
Second feeling that we have got a great faith on God.

34:57.478 --> 34:59.544
When Rama came

34:59.569 --> 35:02.349
people said, we follow Parshuram

35:02.374 --> 35:05.189
when Krishna came, people said, we follow Rama

35:05.214 --> 35:07.435
and now when anyone else will come

35:07.460 --> 35:09.552
people will say that they are following Krishna.

35:09.577 --> 35:12.150
Is Krishna standing in front of you today?

35:12.175 --> 35:14.307
You should also think , who is standing in front of you?

35:14.332 --> 35:16.733
We don't have the trend of being in the present.

35:16.758 --> 35:23.103
To remain in the past thoughts, is to be sentimental

35:23.128 --> 35:28.682
Sentimentalist go so much mad, that we see

35:28.707 --> 35:35.777
both intellectuals and sentimentalists become fanatics.

35:35.802 --> 35:40.443
Fanaticism only gets glued to sentiments

35:40.468 --> 35:44.648
and that feeling becomes too much, it is blind faith

35:44.673 --> 35:45.874
It is blind faith

35:45.899 --> 35:50.015
because of which, man gets glued to one thing

35:50.040 --> 35:52.337
he gets destroyed in his pure desire.

35:52.362 --> 35:55.044
For example, a stream flows down into sand

35:55.069 --> 35:56.213
and comes to an end.

35:56.237 --> 35:58.545
In the same way, our pure desire

35:58.570 --> 36:00.384
is to get one with God.

36:00.409 --> 36:03.186
In the same way, comes to an end in this or that.

36:03.757 --> 36:07.529
In this way, because of our blind faith, there has been great loss.

36:07.554 --> 36:08.823
A great loss!

36:08.848 --> 36:13.387
And the greatest loss is that now by getting separated

36:13.446 --> 36:14.584
have fallen apart.

36:14.609 --> 36:19.981
There is no arrangement of connecting

36:20.006 --> 36:22.903
all that of falling apart, of separation

36:22.928 --> 36:25.739
arrangements of separation have been made.

36:25.764 --> 36:28.129
But when our evolution takes place

36:28.154 --> 36:30.915
You see when our ascent takes place

36:30.940 --> 36:34.366
when we reach our heigher and higher states

36:34.391 --> 36:36.164
integration should take place.

36:36.189 --> 36:38.739
There should be integration.

36:38.764 --> 36:40.579
If integration within us doesn't take place

36:40.604 --> 36:42.700
we should understand that we are falling apart.

36:42.725 --> 36:45.006
If for getting our integration

36:45.031 --> 36:47.109
something has to be done, should be done

36:47.134 --> 36:51.184
and there is only one way for integration and that is Atma.

36:51.209 --> 36:52.985
As soon as we get that

36:53.010 --> 36:55.574
when Kundalini comes in contact with the enlightened atma

36:55.599 --> 36:57.364
then everything gets aside

36:57.389 --> 37:01.266
and in that light man sees how beautiful is the other too.

37:01.291 --> 37:03.751
And then he also starts observing

37:03.776 --> 37:08.454
in the collective consciousness, who is the other.

37:08.479 --> 37:13.626
When you are part and parcel of that Virat, who is the other?

37:13.651 --> 37:16.008
What favour we are doing to the other?

37:16.033 --> 37:16.893
Everybody is ours.

37:16.918 --> 37:20.352
They are our hands, our feet and our eyes only.

37:20.377 --> 37:22.637
But the arrangements that we have made

37:22.662 --> 37:24.769
that with one hand you take out your eye

37:24.794 --> 37:27.895
with the other hand cut your nose and yet with another cut your ear.

37:27.920 --> 37:31.433
and then after holding one ear, say we are Dharmic

37:31.458 --> 37:33.160
the other holding his nose, say we are Dharmic

37:33.818 --> 37:35.933
In this there is not even a bit of dharma.

37:35.958 --> 37:38.066
When a person gets involved in fanaticism

37:38.091 --> 37:40.423
he should know that there is not even a bit of dharma in it.

37:40.448 --> 37:42.891
Till you do not have integrated knowledge

37:42.916 --> 37:45.817
that comes only with the light of the Spirit.

37:45.842 --> 37:49.598
Nobody, none of the saints said

37:49.623 --> 37:52.460
that don't get your realization

37:52.485 --> 37:54.112
otherwise, today

37:54.137 --> 37:56.690
had there been even a single person like that by mistake,

37:56.715 --> 37:58.799
people would have publicly announced.

37:58.824 --> 38:02.718
But by God's grace, how much did they tolerate.

38:02.743 --> 38:07.173
They always said, get your realization.

38:07.198 --> 38:11.328
To get this realization we do many things.

38:11.353 --> 38:15.926
In Sahajyoga we see that, many type of people come in every country.

38:15.951 --> 38:18.952
The dacoits and plunderers who had gone from here

38:18.977 --> 38:22.798
they in their saintly attire, made fool of people

38:22.823 --> 38:24.751
and by making fool of them

38:24.776 --> 38:28.102
they were even told that if you take GANJA, you will know God.

38:28.127 --> 38:30.182
The poor ones take GANJA ( intoxicated drink ) also.

38:32.486 --> 38:34.487
Their blind faith is so much that

38:34.512 --> 38:35.977
they are ready to do, whatever they are told to do.

38:36.002 --> 38:38.505
Somebody told them,"You undress yourself, you will meet God".

38:38.530 --> 38:39.693
They undressed themselves.

38:39.718 --> 38:43.289
So in this way, everywhere if you observe

38:43.314 --> 38:47.742
you can see that every type of compulsion

38:47.767 --> 38:53.069
and a blind man is forcibly put  into a well

38:53.094 --> 38:57.320
and when the well is constructed twenty five people engage in

38:57.345 --> 39:01.481
it is but natural that there can be a big outbreak

39:01.506 --> 39:04.696
because of that there can be a great conflict

39:04.721 --> 39:06.579
because of that, there can be a fight.

39:06.604 --> 39:08.664
Not only this, there can be severe violence as well.

39:08.689 --> 39:10.967
In this way, throw everyone into well

39:10.992 --> 39:13.008
and occupied and possessed it

39:13.033 --> 39:14.799
that we are abbeys of this monastery

39:14.824 --> 39:16.177
we are the Pope of this place

39:16.202 --> 39:19.168
we are so and so of this place.

39:19.193 --> 39:25.289
Even a very great boon of Zen started by Viditama

39:25.314 --> 39:26.895
which is highly valuable

39:26.920 --> 39:29.867
and he would talk at a very great level.

39:29.892 --> 39:32.430
But I saw their leaders

39:32.455 --> 39:33.949
their Kundalini was lying at the base

39:33.974 --> 39:34.507
and they were not even realized.

39:34.532 --> 39:35.639
I asked them how are you ZEN?

39:35.664 --> 39:37.410
The meaning of ZEN is

39:37.435 --> 39:41.387
Z means 'GYANA', means who knows

39:41.412 --> 39:43.526
I asked them, where are you sitting?

39:43.551 --> 39:44.628
How is it?

39:44.653 --> 39:47.035
He said, we have twenty six Kashyaps.

39:47.060 --> 39:48.620
Since then there has been no Kashyap.

39:48.645 --> 39:49.988
How could I be so?

39:50.013 --> 39:52.191
All this came to an end in twelfth century.

39:52.216 --> 39:53.422
There were total twenty six.

39:53.447 --> 39:55.339
I asked him , "Why are you then sitting on that seat?"

39:55.364 --> 39:57.122
"You are sitting on this seat."

39:57.147 --> 39:58.444
"And what is your right?"

39:58.469 --> 40:00.266
In the same way, it is of 'VEDA'.

40:00.291 --> 40:02.449
In 'VEDA' it is written in the first shaloka itself

40:02.474 --> 40:05.641
the one who gets ' VIDA' has the right to 'VEDA'.

40:05.666 --> 40:08.257
The one who doesn't have 'VIDA'

40:08.282 --> 40:11.586
one who hasn't experienced, how is 'VED' going to help him.

40:11.611 --> 40:14.074
What is the meaning of having 'VIDA'?

40:14.099 --> 40:18.285
'VIDA' means the knowledge of consciousness that is inside us.

40:18.310 --> 40:20.114
If we say in English

40:20.139 --> 40:23.832
it is on our central nervous system, we must know our spirit.

40:23.857 --> 40:27.339
If we don't know it on our central nervous system

40:27.364 --> 40:28.981
it is not VIDA ( pure  knowledge on our central nervous system).

40:29.006 --> 40:33.259
All that we have acquired in our evolution

40:33.284 --> 40:36.947
all that we observe on our central nervous system.

40:36.972 --> 40:41.005
By self realization, how much we are benifitted

40:41.030 --> 40:42.979
many, limitless, I can't tell you.

40:43.004 --> 40:48.059
But tomorrow I will tell you what are the advantages of this.

40:48.084 --> 40:50.604
Because, a man first of all checks advantages.

40:50.629 --> 40:54.434
This a mother must know that children take first of all, chocolates.

40:54.459 --> 40:57.386
So, first benifit them and then make them understand

40:57.436 --> 41:00.559
that by progressing forward like this

41:00.584 --> 41:01.913
you can help others also to be benifitted.

41:01.938 --> 41:08.911
When others get benifitted, then you can understand the reality

41:08.936 --> 41:11.337
what you have acquired from Sahajyoga?

41:11.362 --> 41:13.817
Till then you feel that i am selfish

41:13.842 --> 41:16.313
that i am for myself only, i take care of myself only

41:16.338 --> 41:17.959
i can't do anything for others.

41:17.984 --> 41:22.464
When you start giving it to others, then you feel the real joy.

41:22.489 --> 41:25.006
In our country, we have lot of controvercies.

41:25.031 --> 41:26.497
People have raised controvercies

41:26.522 --> 41:28.208
over each and every great incarnation.

41:28.233 --> 41:30.242
But the reality nobody knows.

41:30.267 --> 41:34.158
For example, may be in Geeta, they did not talk about Kundalini

41:34.183 --> 41:36.439
because it was not the time to discuss about it.

41:36.464 --> 41:38.594
But they made it clear that

41:38.619 --> 41:42.665
"Yogakshema vahamyam", first get your yoga and then kshema.

41:42.690 --> 41:45.684
Such an organization is from time immemorial

41:45.709 --> 41:47.380
which bestowed this union of God.

41:47.405 --> 41:50.495
Here in Maharashtra, there was Nath Sampraday

41:50.520 --> 41:53.047
which granted people this union of God.

41:53.072 --> 41:56.489
But just one or two people would get realization those days.

41:56.514 --> 41:59.068
You know during the time of Raja Janaka

